cs.CR, cs.DB, cs.LG, cs.SE, cs.DC 

This paper discusses the use of blockchain technology to improve the integrity and transparency of data in supply chain management, which is a topic related to computer security (cs.CR) and database systems (cs.DB). The paper also proposes a model for the decentralization of the supply chain traceability process, which involves machine learning (cs.LG) and software engineering (cs.SE) techniques. Finally, the implementation of blockchain technology requires distributed computing (cs.DC) concepts.
